oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Mule-drawn Coca-Cola wagon
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of Landan Smith on a mule-drawn Coca-Cola wagon. There is an unidentified man standing next to the wagon. The wagon is in front of Mack's Saloon on a dirt road.
Mack's Saloon was operated by Charles McClelland.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Carts & wagons; Mules; Bars; Streets; Stores & shops; Carbonated beverages
